Also, some games (mostly early ones) use a "negative" Y scroll value to push the whole screen down 1 scanline, to compensate for the way sprites work. Maybe your emulator is not handling the Y scroll properly in those cases?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Mon May 16, 2011 6:20 pm</p><hr />
