<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=7757&amp;p=78240#p78240"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Sprite positions issue]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=7757&amp;p=78240#p78240"><![CDATA[
Positions should be one pixel below what the Y coordinate byte says it should be.  So a sprite at position 8.8 is actually at 8,9.  No sprites are ever drawn in visible scanline 0.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Mon May 16, 2011 1:06 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
